#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.isnan.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.isnan"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isnan.isnan:1 of
msgid "Test element-wise for NaN and return result as a boolean tensor."
msgstr "逐元素测试是否为 NaN，并将结果作为布尔张量返回。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isnan.isnan of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isnan.isnan:3 of
msgid "Input tensor."
msgstr "输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isnan.isnan:5 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可以广播到输入形状。如果未提供或"
"为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isnan.isnan:10 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isnan.isnan of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isnan.isnan:15 of
msgid ""
"**y** -- For scalar input, the result is a new boolean with value True if"
" the input is NaN; otherwise the value is False.  For array input, the "
"result is a boolean tensor of the same dimensions as the input and the "
"values are True if the corresponding element of the input is NaN; "
"otherwise the values are False."
msgstr ""
"**y** —— 对于标量输入，如果输入是 NaN，则结果是一个值为 True 的新布尔值；"
"否则值为 False。对于数组输入，结果是一个与输入维度相同的布尔张量，如果"
"输入的对应元素是 NaN，则值为 True；否则值为 False。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isnan.isnan:15 of
msgid ""
"**y** -- For scalar input, the result is a new boolean with value True if"
" the input is NaN; otherwise the value is False."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isnan.isnan:18 of
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"For array input, the result is a boolean tensor of the same dimensions as"
" the input and the values are True if the corresponding element of the "
"input is NaN; otherwise the values are False."
msgstr ""
"**y** —— 对于标量输入，如果输入是 NaN，则结果是一个值为 True 的新布尔值；"
"否则值为 False。对于数组输入，结果是一个与输入维度相同的布尔张量，如果"
"输入的对应元素是 NaN，则值为 True；否则值为 False。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isnan.isnan of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isnan.isnan:24 of
msgid ""
":py:obj:`isinf`, :py:obj:`isneginf`, :py:obj:`isposinf`, "
":py:obj:`isfinite`, :py:obj:`isnat`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isnan.isnan:27 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.isnan.isnan:28 of
msgid ""
"MaxFrame uses the IEEE Standard for Binary Floating-Point for Arithmetic "
"(IEEE 754). This means that Not a Number is not equivalent to infinity."
msgstr ""
"MaxFrame 使用 IEEE 二进制浮点数算术标准（IEEE 754）。这意味着“非数字”（"
"NaN）不等同于无穷大。"

